<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4529660>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dorsal (A) and ventral (B) views of female holotype of Occidozyga berbeza sp. nov. (SRC 00022 (former KUHE 53037)). Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
